title: The NYT Finally Found Antifa | Guest: Catherine Engelbrecht | 10/5/20
description:
The media is mad that President Trump and Secret Service agents took a “joy ride.” Despite what the media says, stats from the CDC and WHO prove that the U.S. is far from the most coronavirus-stricken country. "60 Minutes" aired an episode on Biden accuser Tara Reade in Australia, but not the U.S. A speech from a Baltimore Ravens player shows the power of the nuclear family. The New York Times has finally found Antifa, or at least “insurrection anarchists.” Catherine Engelbrecht, founder & president of True the Vote, discusses how Biden’s Texas political director was implicated in a mail-in ballot scheme. Make sure to register to vote! Take the Left at their word when they suggest revolutionary changes. The Pope is criticizing free market economics.
